FINDDEPSLINKED(1) General Commands Manual FINDDEPSLINKED(1)

NAME

finddepslinked — find linked dependencies for a package

SYNOPSIS

finddepslinked [-hv] pkgname

DESCRIPTION

The finddepslinked utility lists the dependencies of the installed package's dynamic executables and libraries. It operates on installed packages and requires ldd(1), pkginfo(1) and pkgman(1).

The options are as follows:

-v, --version
Print version and exit.
-h, --help
Print help and exit.

SEE ALSO

finddepsdistmeta(1), finddisappeared(1), finddisowned(1), findredundantdeps(1)
